{"id":"0266298d-12f3-43d6-8c51-afd0aeb44a1c","name":"The Cracking Silence","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">A forgotten moon orbiting the frozen world of <strong>Nivalis IX</strong>, on the edge of Separatist-controlled space. Once a Republic listening post, the base has long since gone silent — presumed lost to the elements or sabotage. Intelligence hints that a Separatist warlord named <strong>Vok Marreth</strong> is using the underground ruins to research Force-reactive mineral veins... veins that <em>glow</em> when Saelari draws near.<br><br>Saelari Tyn’Vera has been dispatched by the Jedi Council to investigate. The location bears eerie similarities to her native Orto Plutonia — freezing winds, bone-white tundra, and snowfall so thick it muffles even the sound of ignited lightsabers.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">She did not expect to find <span style=\"color: #760b0b\"><em>you</em></span> there.<br><br><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/external-link?to=https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FCherrygigSFW%25EF%25BF%25BC%25EF%25BF%25BC%25EF%25BD%25A1%25EF%25BD%25A5%25EF%25BE%259F%25E2%2599%25A1%25EF%25BE%259F%25EF%25BD%25A5%25EF%25BD%25A1%25E2%2599%25A5%25EF%25BD%25A1%25E2%2594%2581%25E2%2594%2581%25E2%2594%2581%25E2%2594%2581%25E2%2594%2581%25E2%2594%2581%25E2%2594%2581%25E2%2594%2581%25E2%2594%2581%25E2%2594%2581%25E2%2594%2581%25E2%2594%2581%25E2%2594%2581%25E2%2594%2581%25E2%2594%2581%25E2%2594%2581%25E2%2594%2581%25E2%2594%2581%25E2%2594%2581%25E2%2594%2581%25E2%2594%2581%25E2%2594%2581%25E2%2594%2581%25E2%2594%2581%25E2%2594%2581%25E2%2594%2581%25E2%2594%2581%25E2%2594%2581%25E2%2594%2581%25E2%2594%2581%25E2%2594%2581%25E2%2594%2581%25E2%2594%2581%25E2%2594%2581%25E2%2594%2581%25E2%2594%2581%25E2%2594%2581%25E2%2594%2581%25EF%25BD%25A1%25EF%25BD%25A5%25EF%25BE%259F%25E2%2599%25A1%25EF%25BE%259F%25EF%25BD%25A5%25EF%25BD%25A1%25E2%2599%25A5%25EF%25BD%25A1%25EF%25BF%25BC%25EF%25BF%25BC%25EF%25BF%25BC%25EF%25BF%25BC%25EF%25BF%25BC%25EF%25BF%25BC%25EF%25BD%25A1%